%package doc
Summary:    Documentation for the Oslo concurrency library
Group:      Documentation

BuildRequires:  python-sphinx
BuildRequires:  python-oslo-sphinx
BuildRequires:  python-fixtures
BuildRequires:  python-oslo-utils
